UPDATE V2_2 : http://css.gamebanana.com/maps/175523	

Offical escape map of the movie indiana jones and the crystal skull.

This map is divided in 3 levels of game and two levels of difficulty.

> Level 1 : Desert.

> Level 2 : Forest

> Level 3 : Temple

Remake all levels in Extreme difficulty (zombie with 50000 HP, and others  things)

In this map the main goal is to find the crystal skull and put it in the temple.

You can win this map if you kill a boss alien
Your server must to have a noblock plugin

You can contact me on my e-mail : biohazard@dreamevo.fr or on my team website : www.dreamevo.fr

Thank you for download






##### EDIT : CAUTION: THE CRASH OF PLAYERS CAN COME FROM A TOO HIGHT ENTITIES NUMBERS IN THE MAP. TO PREVENT A CRASH OF ANY PLAYER DOES NOT EXCEED 40 PLAYERS ON THE MAP. I WILL BE FIX THIS FAIL IN THE NEXT FIX.
